{"tid":628150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【警偷妓女錢】兩警掃黃後　涉警署內盜被捕妓女三千元　高層震怒","createTime":"2018-04-13T14:33:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T06:08:02.000Z","uid":5195,"like":178,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"6053381ee2f108c8aeb3dc98f6344ac428da474f","tid":628150,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T14:33:43.000Z","msg":"警隊發生監守自盜案件，兩名警員執行掃黃任務時，疑盜取一名妓女3000元現金，最終被揭發，一同被捕。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，兩名被捕警員駐守東區警區特別職務隊。警方及入境處昨日在東區進行一項聯合掃黃行動，拘捕多名涉案女子，並帶返警署調查。期間，有人懷疑將疑犯身上物件放起收入袋時，趁無人為意，盜去其中一名疑犯銀包內的3000元現金，再放入自己褲袋，其後再將贓款交予另一人。<br />\n<br />\n該名女疑犯其後發現失竊，於是向警員舉報。警方翻查閉路電視片段後，揭發有同僚犯案，於是將兩名涉案者拘捕。案件現交由港島總區重案組跟進。據了解，掃黃行動在昨午進行，其後涉案警員再外出繼續掃黃行動，晚上返警署後被揭發事件，遭問話後被捕，事件令警隊高層震怒。"},{"pid":"0ef390f3c28148e9ed06e293dcc624502f0afb54","tid":628150,"uid":609,"like":77,"dislike":1,"score":76,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T14:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 專業喎 守法喎"},{"pid":"39d706d0e3545e870e71bd28d31431b70f27d353","tid":628150,"uid":82532,"like":73,"dislike":1,"score":72,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T14:35:45.000Z","msg":"高層震怒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad90c845f19ec0a4f7dd3f2d100000b035eaf1e","tid":628150,"uid":103235,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T14:36:45.000Z","msg":"為咗嗰三千蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdb97665964bba56cb0e445bcef8dbabd884c51b","tid":628150,"uid":17765,"like":91,"dislike":0,"score":91,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T14:36:54.000Z","msg":"食完又拎<br />\n賤撚過雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b14c33a3da1bfee8b9b281b34b65d020b80c8ca4","tid":628150,"uid":365